<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīramey tuṇaiyāka tiyākamey <unclear>A</unclear>ṇaiyākac ce(ce)ṅko loccik karuṅkali kaṭintu veṇku<note n="372-2">The right end of the inscription is very much damaged.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>kācanattu viṟṟirun=ta ruḷina ko<hi rend="grantha">rā ja</hi>ke<supplied reason="omitted">ca</supplied>ripaṉmarāna Uṭaiyār <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> vīra<hi rend="grantha">rājentra-</hi> tevarkku yāṇṭu 3<g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>Āvatu <hi rend="grantha">rā je</hi>(n)<hi rend="grantha">ntr(ā)</hi> coḻava <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>ṭṭu vāvalū<unclear>r</unclear>nāṭṭu tevatānam tiruvāmāttūruṭaiya parama<hi rend="grantha">svāmi</hi> kaḷukku coḻamaṇṭalattuk keraḷān=ta kavaḷanā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/><hi rend="grantha">jāśra</hi> yacatu<hi rend="grantha">rvve</hi> timaṅkalattu peṇṭāṭṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> <unclear>ka</unclear>ccāniyāna pulokakaṟpa<unclear>kam</unclear> vaitta tiru<unclear>nu</unclear>n=tā viḷakku Onṟukku vai <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>l tuḷainiṟai cempoṉ patinkaḻiñcu Ippoṉ patinkaḻañcuṅ koṇṭu Ittirunu- n=tā viḷakku muṭṭāmai Erikka<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>kaṭavomā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/>ṇāḻikai <hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi> yomu Ivaṉey Ikkoyil Āṭava<supplied reason="omitted">l</supplied>lāṟku cātta Iṭṭa <unclear>po</unclear>ṟkāṟai Iraṇṭināl muttum kottu tu <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ḷ kotta nāl <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>lā cempon muppatteḻu kaḻañcey kāley munṟumāvum tirukkaikkāṟai Iraṇṭiṉāl muttum muttukkotta nūlu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="8"/><unclear>nūlu</unclear>m Arakkum Uṭpaṭṭa cempon meṟpaṭikallāl niṟai muppatu nāṟkaḻañcey mukkāley Iraṇṭumañcāṭiyu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>niṟai Eḻupattiru kaḻañcey Iraṇṭumañcāṭiyum <unclear>nā</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">ṉ</supplied>māvaraiyum Ivaṉe vaitta nilaiviḷakku nāṟcāṇarai Ucarattu niṟai I <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
